uld be one "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}]}}}